---
import BentoItem from './BentoItem.astro';
---

<section
  class={`
    w-full max-w-[1400px]
    grid grid-cols-10 auto-rows-[30rem] gap-4
    mx-auto p-20
  `}
>
  <BentoItem
    class="col-span md:col-span-4"
    title="ANDORRA: EL CENIT DE LOS PREMIOS ESLAND"
  >
    <div
      slot="image"
      class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0
        h-full group-hover:scale-110 transition-scale duration-1000
        ease-in-ou opacity-90 bg-blend-luminosity bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-blue-950 -z-10"
      style="background-image: url('/mountain.png')"
    >
    </div>
    <p slot="content" class="max-w-xl">
      Este a√±o, el momento de la alfombra azul sera sustituido y mejorado,
      gracias a los increibles paisajes andorranos, por una <strong
        >alfombra blanca en plena nieve</strong
      >, situada en las <strong>pistas de esqui de Andorra</strong>
    </p>
  </BentoItem>
  <BentoItem
    class="col-span md:col-span-6"
    title="LA ALFOMBRA BLANCA"
    subtitle="16 de Febrero de 2024"
  >
    <div
      slot="image"
      class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0
        h-full group-hover:scale-110 transition-scale duration-1000
        ease-in-ou opacity-90 bg-blend-luminosity bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-blue-950 -z-10"
      style="background-image: url('/mountain.png')"
    >
    </div>
  </BentoItem>
  <BentoItem
    class="col-span md:col-span-6"
    title="LA GALA"
    subtitle="17 de Febrero de 2024"
  >
    <div
      slot="image"
      class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0
        h-full group-hover:scale-110 transition-scale duration-1000
        ease-in-ou opacity-90 bg-blend-luminosity bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-blue-950 -z-10"
      style="background-image: url('/mountain.png')"
    >
    </div>
  </BentoItem>
  <BentoItem
    class="col-span md:col-span-4"
    title="DISFRUTA DEL REDDIT DE LA COMUNIDAD"
  >
    <div
      slot="image"
      class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0
        h-full group-hover:scale-110 transition-scale duration-1000
        ease-in-ou opacity-90 bg-blend-luminosity bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-blue-950 -z-10"
      style="background-image: url('/mountain.png')"
    >
    </div>
  </BentoItem>
</section>
